setDictionary

void setDictionary(AutoCompleteDictionary dict)
Set the dictionary that autocomplete lookup should be performed by.

Parameters:
dict - The dictionary that will be used for the autocomplete lookups. The dictionary implemetation should be very fast at lookups to avoid delays as the user types.
